data.description: Welcome home!  Feel right at home as you enter this atrium ranch nestled within the prestigious Parkway West School District. Boasting 3 generous bedrooms and 2 beautifully updated baths, this home seamlessly combines comfort and convenience. Main floor laundry adds to the relaxed living provided in this home. With extra living space in the basement, the possibilities are endless – from a cozy media room to a home gym or play area. Let's not forget the pièce de résistance – the atrium area in the middle of the home, complete with a newer spa, offering a serene retreat perfect for star gazing or your morning coffee. In addition, the backyard fence and deck are maintenance free. HSA Warranty provided. Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac in the coveted Glan Tai subdivision, residents enjoy exclusive access to a neighborhood pool and a plethora of fun-filled activities year round. Don't miss your chance to make this home your reality – schedule a viewing today and prepare to fall in love.
